# 5G Core Networks

## Overview

This assignment explored the architecture of modern 5G core networks, comparing them with LTE EPC while examining Network Slicing, Multi-access Edge Computing (MEC), and Network Repository Functions (NRF).

## Technologies

- 5G Core
- MEC
- Network Slicing

## Skills Developed

- 5G architecture
- Network virtualization
- Cloud-native networking

## Learning Outcome

The assignment demonstrated how modern mobile networks improve flexibility, scalability, and service delivery.
